"Test #deq — doble igualdad
'<hr/>
"1. Escalar
#deq σ = M*c/I = P*L*c/(4*I)

'<hr/>
"2. Vector
#deq F = [F_1; F_2; M_1] = [P; V; M]

'<hr/>
"3. Matriz
#deq K = [k_1; 0; 0 | 0; k_2; k_3 | 0; k_3; k_4] = [EA/L; 0; 0 | 0; 12*EI/L^3; 6*EI/L^2 | 0; 6*EI/L^2; 4*EI/L]

'<hr/>
"4. Ecuación P = K · δ
#deq P = K*δ = [EA/L; 0; 0 | 0; 12*EI/L^3; 6*EI/L^2 | 0; 6*EI/L^2; 4*EI/L]*[δ_1; δ_2; δ_3]

'<hr/>
"5. Triple igualdad
#deq f(x) = a*x^2 + b*x + c = 0
